OL,3,CFly-and-drink-drivers targeted as
OL,4,Cfamily faces Christmas without baby
OL,5,Cand aunt
OL,7,FAnderson was also heading home, to
OL,8,FRotherham, in South Yorkshire,
OL,9,Fstraight from a flight and at three
OL,10,Ftimes the limit.
OL,12,FPrompted by the deaths of Zackary and
OL,13,FKarlene, Durham Constabulary have
OL,14,Fjoined up with Northumbria Police to
OL,15,Flaunch a campaign warning people not
OL,16,Fto be tempted to get behind the wheel
OL,17,Fif they have had a mid-air drink.
OL,19,FDetective Natalie Horner, from the
OL,20,Fforce's serious collision unit,
OL,21,Fattended the scene of the crash in May.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/11
