OL,4,Cfamily faces Christmas without baby
OL,5,Cand aunt
OL,7,FShe told ITV Tyne Tees: "We see it all
OL,8,Fthe time but this year it just felt
OL,9,Fdifferent - the loss of Zackary and
OL,10,FKarlene in such horrific circumstances.
OL,12,F"They've never been the same and
OL,13,Fthey're never going to be the same
OL,14,Fagain and they're suffering every day.
OL,15,FFor that reason alone I will continue
OL,16,Fand the team I work with - we will
OL,17,Fcontinue to do more to stop it from
OL,18,Fhappening to someone else."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/11
