OL,4,Cfamily faces Christmas without baby
OL,5,Cand aunt
OL,7,FDetective Horner said the deaths of
OL,8,Fbaby Zackary and Karlene, from County
OL,9,FDurham, had been "personal" and in the
OL,10,Fwake of the crash the force was left
OL,11,Fthinking about what more could be done
OL,12,Fto prevent further fatalities.
OL,14,FTargeting drivers at Newcastle Airport
OL,15,Fon Thursday (19 December) as part of
OL,16,FOperation Takeoff was "for them and
OL,17,Fthe greater public".
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/11
