OL,5,Cand aunt
OL,7,FShe continued: "I don't want anyone
OL,8,Felse killed in a road death. I've had
OL,9,Fto knock on too many doors. I've had
OL,10,Fto take people to far too many
OL,11,Fmortuaries to see their loved ones.
OL,12,FIt's them people we're doing it for
OL,13,Ftoday."
OL,15,FInspector Simon Hogg was one of the
OL,16,Ffirst officers at the roadside in the
OL,17,Faftermath of the A1 collision, which
OL,18,Fis understood to have left 100
OL,19,Fofficers requiring trauma counselling.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/11
