OL,4,Cfamily faces Christmas without baby
OL,5,Cand aunt
OL,7,FSpeaking to ITV Tyne Tees, Insp Hogg
OL,8,Fdescribed how he and his "colleagues
OL,9,Fhad blood on their hands at the scene
OL,10,Fand were deeply affected" by what they
OL,11,Fencountered.
OL,13,F"It has a huge effect," he said. "I
OL,14,Fdon't have a problem admitting I was
OL,15,Fupset and spoke to my wife about it
OL,16,Fwhen I got home. It was horrific, just
OL,17,Fhorrific.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/11
