OL,3,CFly-and-drink-drivers targeted as
OL,4,Cfamily faces Christmas without baby
OL,5,Cand aunt
OL,7,F"But that was nothing compared to what
OL,8,Fthe family have gone through. That's
OL,9,Fwhat made us think that's an issue we
OL,10,Freally need to highlight. Because that
OL,11,Fdriver had just stepped off the plane
OL,12,Fand was three times the limit."
OL,14,FThe force will target drivers at both
OL,15,FNewcastle Airport and Teesside Airport
OL,16,Fas part of the campaign, which is
OL,17,Fhoped will be rolled out across the
OL,18,Fcountry.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/11
