OL,3,CFly-and-drink-drivers targeted as
OL,4,Cfamily faces Christmas without baby
OL,5,Cand aunt
OL,7,FBy raising more awareness of the
OL,8,Fissue, it is hoped the act of flying,
OL,9,Fdrinking and driving will become
OL,10,F"socially unacceptable".
OL,12,FInsp Hogg added: "It's probably more
OL,13,Fcommon than we realise where people
OL,14,Fhave a few drinks at the airport and
OL,15,Fthen get on the plane, potentially
OL,16,Fforgetting that they're going to have
OL,17,Fto drive when they get to the other
OL,18,Fside.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G9/11
