OL,3,CFly-and-drink-drivers targeted as
OL,4,Cfamily faces Christmas without baby
OL,5,Cand aunt
OL,7,F"Well me and my team have seen first
OL,8,Fhand the devastating consequences of
OL,9,Fthat when a drink driver destroys a
OL,10,Ffamily and we just thought that needed
OL,11,Fhighlighting.
OL,13,F"That's the purpose of this campaign -
OL,14,Fto raise awareness of that and make it
OL,15,Fas equally socially unacceptable as
OL,16,Fdrink-driving."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G10/11
