OL,4,Cfamily faces Christmas without baby
OL,5,Cand aunt
OL,7,FOut of 80 people breathalysed at the
OL,8,Fairport today, all drivers tested
OL,9,Fnegative for being over the drink-
OL,10,Fdrive limit. Two of them had alcohol
OL,11,Fin their system but were below the
OL,12,Flegal limit.
OL,14,FThey were given advice and a warning
OL,15,Fabout how long alcohol can stay in the
OL,16,Fbody.
OL,18,FDarryl Anderson was jailed for more
OL,19,Fthan 17 years for causing death by
OL,20,Fdangerous driving.
